### 1. Submit KPI for Goal 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/kpis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "goalId": 1,
  "targetValue": 100.00,
  "actualValue": 95.00,
  "period": "2026-Q1",
  "notes": "Great progress on test coverage"
}

### 2. Submit KPI for Goal 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/kpis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "goalId": 2,
  "targetValue": 100.00,
  "actualValue": 75.00,
  "period": "2026-Q1",
  "notes": "Some delays in sprint"
}

### 3. Update existing KPI (upsert)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/kpis
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "goalId": 1,
  "targetValue": 100.00,
  "actualValue": 98.00,
  "period": "2026-Q1",
  "notes": "Updated progress"
}

### 4. Get KPI by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/kpis/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get KPI not found (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/kpis/999
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get KPIs by Goal
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/kpis/goal/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Get KPIs by User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/kpis/user/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Get KPIs by Period
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/kpis/period/2026-Q1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}